column4: Welcome, you are now talking to an AI doctor. As I am part of a scientific experiment, I would appreciate it if you could take the time to answer a super short questionnaire at the end of the interview. Tap Speak to ask your question and then tap Send to submit it to me.
What can I help you with today? What symptoms are you experiencing?
Are you experiencing any other symptoms such asshortness of breath, sore throat, coughing, fever, chills, or achy body?
I'm sorry, I don't understand what you said. Please try rephrasing your question.
I'm sorry, I don't understand what you said. Please try rephrasing your question in English.
I'm sorry, I still don't understand what you said. Could you please restate your question in English so I can help you?
I'm sorry, I still don't understand what you said. Could you please restate your question so I can understand and help you?
